              mkd:NathanYoung, mkd:RaulDeMaldonado, mkd:SelinaMeyer ;
    rdfs:comment """Year 1 student, part-time kindergarten worker, 
    and occasional builder of RDF vocabularies about herself. 
    Subtly interested in the moons of the outer solar system and whether 
    anything is swimming in Europa's ocean. Also very interested in etymology and karaoke. 
    Will most definitely overuse the rdfs:comment thingy, I should know better. 
    Too much of anything is..."""@en ;
    rdfs:seeAlso <https://mudoki.github.io/kg-lab2-folio/terms#> .
    
    
